### **Substantial Holder Notice – Key Details**  

- **Substantial Holder:** TAL Dai-ichi Life Australia Pty Ltd (TAL) & Dai-ichi Life Holdings (associates).  
- **Transaction Date:** 16 June 2025.  
- **Shares Acquired:** 33,234,618 fully paid ordinary shares in Challenger Limited (CGF).  
- **Seller:** AP Liberty GP, LLC (general partner of AP Liberty, L.P.).  
- **Purchase Price:** **AUD 247.6 million** (~AUD 7.45 per share).  
- **Resulting Stake:** **19.90%** (up from ~15.09% previously).  
- **Conditional Agreement:** Subject to regulatory approvals (implied by "conditional").  

*No other material information identified.*
